note on link #F5F5F5
  All business modules
  perform read/write
  on MongoDB
end note

'================================================
' REALTIME PIPELINE
'   Allocation / Registration
'   в†’ Notification Center
'   в†’ Socket.IO
'   в†’ WebSocket в†’ Client
